column334:
Vanganga Garden is one of the best places to visit in Silvassa if you wish to spend some time in the lap of nature. It is stretched across an area of 7.5 hectares and has paved walkways for running in different directions. Different varieties of trees and plants are clustered in the garden area that makes it look like a mini forest. You can also spot small fountains in the garden that look extremely spellbinding in the evening due to the lighting arrangement.

It also has a beautiful lake that is framed with a jogging track and a few restaurants for recreational purposes. You can enjoy boating on the lake, or you can even head to the garden to have a picnic or family outing.

Lion Safari is good Place for Animals and Nature Lover.
At present one lioness in the lion Safari. Few years ago I visited lion Safari, there were total four lion and lioness.
I had seen lioness from very nearly.(6 to 7 feets away) It was amazing moment.
I appreciate best efforts and arrangement of Forest Department for taking care for visitors safety.
There is a small children playing area near main entry gate of lion Safari, kids can take benefits of these facilities during waiting period.
One Big tree is also one of attraction at lion safari.
Entry Ticket fees for one adult person is only 25 Rupees. it's very reasonable.
Waiting Period for visit is 20 minutes to 1 hour. It's depend upon total numbers of visitor and timing of visit.
Personally I Suggest, try to arrange visit at 10 am.Everyday lion Safari opens for visit at 10 am.
Every Monday it's remain close for visit.
